                    </div>

                    <h2 class="fs-3 text-body">Programme Overview</h2>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        ILM Academy’s <b>TOEFL Preparation Course</b> is tailored for students aiming for higher education abroad and professionals seeking global opportunities.
                        The course focuses on <em>academic English, test strategies, and skill development</em> across all four modules—Reading, Listening, Speaking, and Writing.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Learners will build strong comprehension, analytical, and communication skills to meet the demands of international universities. Our experienced trainers ensure students gain the confidence to achieve high scores in TOEFL.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="fs-3 text-body mb-3">Entry Requirements</h3>
                    <div class="bg-light rounded-3 p-4 mb-4">
                        <p>Basic English proficiency required.</p>
                        <p>Recommended for students planning for study abroad and professionals aiming for international careers.</p>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="fs-3 text-body mb-3">Programme Structure</h3>
                    <p>The TOEFL Preparation Course covers the following areas:</p>
                    <ul class="list-style-one">
                        <li>Reading comprehension strategies for academic texts</li>
                        <li>Listening skills with focus on lectures & conversations</li>
                        <li>Writing practice for essays and integrated tasks</li>
                        <li>Speaking sessions with feedback and mock interviews</li>
                        <li>Time management techniques for test day</li>
                        <li>Regular mock tests & performance analysis</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        By the end of the course, students will have the skills and confidence to achieve competitive TOEFL scores and pursue their study abroad goals.
                    </p>
                </div>

